WEBVTT

00:00:16.559 --> 00:00:22.559
This was made at the Bethel, this magazine too.

00:00:23.559 --> 00:00:29.559
Here at Bethel, Bibles in many kinds of Bible-based publications are produced.

00:00:30.559 --> 00:00:33.560
How are these publications produced?

00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:40.560
The original scripts in English are sent from the World Headquarters of Jehovah's Witnesses in New York

00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:45.560
and then are translated into Japanese by a translation team.

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:52.560
The translated scripts are neatly composed using maps, which was developed by Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:58.560
The composed electronic data are burned onto printing plates and sent for printing.

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:09.000
A tremendous amount of white paper will be turned into Bibles in publications containing the vital message.

00:02:14.740 --> 00:02:21.740
This Bible literature is shipped continuously to meet the spiritual needs of people all over the world.

00:02:25.389 --> 00:02:32.389
As we ship out box after box, we think of those who will receive them with happy smiles.

00:02:37.870 --> 00:02:40.870
Can you read the first paragraph please?

00:02:45.710 --> 00:02:48.710
There have been some great opportunities to talk about my beliefs.

00:02:49.710 --> 00:02:56.710
E-publications have also been provided, which you can easily access through the official website of Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:02:57.710 --> 00:03:03.710
Including many sign language programs, a variety of audio video programs has been produced.

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:37.599
To support the activities of Jehovah's Witnesses, various kinds of work are being done here at Bethel, such as preparation for conventions and assemblies.

00:03:37.599 --> 00:03:49.500
Helping with the construction of kingdom halls, providing useful information on bloodless treatment,

00:03:50.500 --> 00:03:53.500
and organizing disaster relief work.

00:03:56.740 --> 00:04:03.139
Here at Bethel, you will see many working zealously, doing all kinds of work.

00:04:04.139 --> 00:04:11.139
All of them are closely united so that they can give full support to our worldwide Bible educational work.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:20.680
We are really pleased to see you here at Bethel.

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:28.680
It has been a privilege to provide you with a glimpse of some of the work being done at the Japan branch.
